---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Help Center"
  description="Campus XI Help Center with common answers and direct support form."
>
  <section class="hero-panel hero-panel--single">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Support</p>
      <h1>Help Center</h1>
      <p class="hero-text">
        Use this page for account help, purchase issues, and points questions.
        Send clear details so the team can respond quickly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="section-shell form-shell help-contact-shell"
    id="help-request"
  >
    <div class="form-intro">
      <h2>Send a help request.</h2>
      <a class="text-link" href="#frequently-asked-questions">
        See frequently asked questions
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="form-card">
      <form data-support-form action="/api/support" method="post">
        <input type="hidden" name="requestType" value="help" />

        <div class="form-grid">
          <label>
            Full Name
            <input name="name" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Email Address
            <input type="email" name="email" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Topic
            <select name="topic" required data-prefill="topic">
              <option value="">Select one</option>
              <option value="Account">Account</option>
              <option value="Purchase">Purchase</option>
              <option value="Points">Points</option>
              <option value="Other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label>
            Device
            <select name="device" required>
              <option value="">Select one</option>
              <option value="iPhone">iPhone</option>
              <option value="Android Phone">Android Phone</option>
              <option value="Tablet">Tablet</option>
              <option value="Other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="full">
            Message
            <textarea
              name="message"
              required
              data-prefill="message"
              placeholder="Tell us what you need help with."></textarea>
          </label>
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Send Help Request</button>
        <p class="form-status" aria-live="polite"></p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="section-shell help-faq-shell"
    id="frequently-asked-questions"
  >
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Frequently Asked Questions</p>
      <h2>Open a question to see the answer.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary>I forgot my email. What should I do?</summary>
        <p>
          Use the password reset or account recovery flow for the email you
          normally use. If you are not sure which email is linked to your
          account, contact support and include your team name and any purchase
          details that can help us locate the account.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>I cannot sign in. What should I do?</summary>
        <p>
          Make sure you are using the same sign-in method you used when you
          created the account. For example, if you signed up with Google, you
          need to keep using Google. If you signed up with Apple, use Apple.
          If you use the wrong method, the sign-in may fail or open a different
          account.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>My pass is not showing as active.</summary>
        <p>
          First, try restarting the app and check again. If the pass still does
          not appear as active, share your transaction details and tell us
          whether the purchase was made through Apple or Google Play. Include
          the account email you used in the app so we can verify the purchase
          and activation status.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I request a refund?</summary>
        <p>
          If a purchase was completed and verification was successful, it is
          generally non-refundable. If the purchase went through but
          verification failed, contact support with the purchase details so we
          can review it.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>I cannot edit my team.</summary>
        <p>
          Team editing may be locked because the deadline has passed for that
          round or matchday. Once the deadline closes, changes are restricted
          until the next allowed window.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>I cannot transfer players.</summary>
        <p>
          Transfers may be unavailable when the deadline window is closed. If
          the deadline has passed, wait for the next transfer window.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>My event says not available.</summary>
        <p>
          This could mean the event has not started yet or that it has already
          ended. Check the event timing and availability window first. If it
          still looks wrong, contact support with the event name and the
          account you used.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>I cannot change formation.</summary>
        <p>
          Formation flexibility is a premium feature. Bronze Pass and above let
          you use any formation for your team.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>I cannot set deadline reminders.</summary>
        <p>
          Deadline reminders are part of Tournament Pass features. Bronze Pass
          allows 1 custom deadline reminder per matchday, Silver allows 2, and
          Gold allows 3.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What comes with Bronze Pass?</summary>
        <p>
          Bronze Pass gives you team renaming at any time during the
          tournament, flexible formations, top-5 player tracking each
          matchday, 1 custom deadline reminder per matchday, a premium profile
          and leaderboard badge, improved action limits, rank progression
          badges, and enhanced share card styles.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What comes with Silver Pass?</summary>
        <p>
          Silver Pass includes everything in Bronze, then adds Smart XI for
          suggested lineups and key squad decisions, squad insights, deeper
          manager comparison, live fixture updates during the matchday, full
          published squad history for managers on the leaderboard, 2 custom
          deadline reminders per matchday, and further improved action limits.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What comes with Gold Pass?</summary>
        <p>
          Gold Pass includes everything in Silver, then adds live activity and
          fixture score updates during the matchday, instant alerts for key
          fixture activity, 3 custom deadline reminders per matchday, live
          activities and squads for managers on the leaderboard, leaderboard
          rank progression badges, and the most generous action limits.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="module" src="/scripts/support-form.js"></script>
</SiteLayout>
